{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"4f7fcca5b9","title":"张春桥对上海目前形势的几点看法","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"027d2b88d4","index":0,"year":1967,"month":1,"day":0,"articleId":"4f7fcca5b9"}],"tags":[{"id":"c20d333791","name":"关键人物文稿","type":"文稿大类"},{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"zhangchunqiao","name":"春桥文录","internal":false,"official":true,"type":"pdf","author":"张春桥","files":"/books/zhangchunqiao.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"fae13ac6b9","name":"张春桥"}]},"publication_details":{"zhangchunqiao":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"08ad816b67","type":"title","text":"张春桥对上海目前形势的几点看法","index":0,"publicationId":"zhangchunqiao","articleId":"4f7fcca5b9"},{"id":"cbf22d7ea6","type":"paragraph","text":"一、中心问题：是抓革命，促生产，反对经济主义。","index":1,"publicationId":"zhangchunqiao","articleId":"4f7fcca5b9"},{"id":"aa3c20a410","type":"paragraph","text":"二、造反派要更好地团结群众，建立新的劳动秩序，有些组织有机会主义，如五七年成立派别，五八年成立级别，炊事员成立派别等等，这样会分散阶级队伍，建议工交系统组织阶级队伍。","index":2,"publicationId":"zhangchunqiao","articleId":"4f7fcca5b9"},{"id":"6e8bc47c07","type":"paragraph","text":"三、上山下乡是大方向，应大力宣传？","index":3,"publicationId":"zhangchunqiao","articleId":"4f7fcca5b9"},{"id":"6915c732b6","type":"paragraph","text":"四、多宣传打倒经济主义，就中央反对经济主义的五条，逐条宣传，集中点便是抓革命，促生产。这样可以处于不败之地。可以召开上千人的大会，介绍新的先进事迹。","index":4,"publicationId":"zhangchunqiao","articleId":"4f7fcca5b9"},{"id":"6deed6a1d5","type":"paragraph","text":"五、上海形势，外部矛盾转入内部矛盾，造反派内部打内战，造反派要整风，做到艰苦朴素，接近群众，不要有气，有些组织可以搞些条例。","index":5,"publicationId":"zhangchunqiao","articleId":"4f7fcca5b9"},{"id":"74e41a9e57","type":"paragraph","text":"六、游街多，打击面过广（注：上海最近游斗过多，当权派、保守派等被拉上街），有的出现跪的现象，这本身就是封建主义的东西。","index":6,"publicationId":"zhangchunqiao","articleId":"4f7fcca5b9"},{"id":"d1c976e6fe","type":"paragraph","text":"七、左派掌权，左、中、右都可以使用。不然，左派就会被别人打倒。","index":7,"publicationId":"zhangchunqiao","articleId":"4f7fcca5b9"},{"id":"d312d3e05e","type":"paragraph","text":"八、要做群众工作，接管后，主要问题是生产问题。上海地方关系全局。","index":8,"publicationId":"zhangchunqiao","articleId":"4f7fcca5b9"},{"id":"5b2d4972ff","type":"paragraph","text":"九、造反派要注意团结，在大方向一致下求同，小节可以有异。好好学习《关于正确处理人民内部矛盾的问题》。","index":9,"publicationId":"zhangchunqiao","articleId":"4f7fcca5b9"},{"id":"9730eb3092","type":"paragraph","text":"十、在批判资产阶级反动路线斗争中，北京市中学生要比大学生差二大截。上海也是这样，上海某些中学造反力量很弱。","index":10,"publicationId":"zhangchunqiao","articleId":"4f7fcca5b9"},{"id":"28d77f0cbb","type":"paragraph","text":"（此讲话大致在一月下旬）","index":11,"publicationId":"zhangchunqiao","articleId":"4f7fcca5b9"}],"page":{"id":"f8cfaa42c2","publicationId":"zhangchunqiao","articleId":"4f7fcca5b9","start":74,"end":74}}}},"__N_SSG":true}